{"tid":825841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宣佈停市都停工左一半啦傻鳭林奠","createTime":"2018-09-17T22:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T00:45:56.000Z","uid":70846,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"07e1bcac9cae638226bb9dfe34b528d76f09c6a1","tid":825841,"uid":70846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T22:52:27.000Z","msg":"根本上尋日如果林奠宣佈股市停市、非緊急公務員休假，運房局出嚟講巴士全線未搞掂、地鐵東鐵線未能正常運作，呼籲私人機構休假一天已經搞掂<br />\n<br />\n而家你個股市都冇停過，銀行點撚樣停呀？銀行政府都唔停其他工種點撚會停呀<br />\n<br />\n成班護主犬出嚟做特首冇權力叫人停工 <br />\n<br />\n01都買咗政府其實尋日唔知道地鐵東鐵線跪低架巴士全線收檔。依家係一黎政府柒下柒下乜柒都唔知，二竹黎根本冇作為就係咁簡單，總之林奠無撚用啦"},{"pid":"759b11aa1500dbd7b6b79dadb8c72c2b8b9509b1","tid":825841,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大把冧樹仲係返路邊完全冇人清理"},{"pid":"42c81e18910cb21b0c98c62e5832ee6fb0024bcd","tid":825841,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:18:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家你個股市都冇停過，銀行點撚樣停呀？</blockquote><br />\n啲林鄭fans話咁樣講係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86180d53df0c90781c8fb436360d5b438f13b44d","tid":825841,"uid":53105,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:19:36.000Z","msg":"八達通都唔識用，點會知市民點返工"},{"pid":"48b814da1a8dbf56febe2fa3ab003824c21c781e","tid":825841,"uid":2544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:21:28.000Z","msg":"正一臭西"},{"pid":"5fd3cfd23030b97b073506c74be0a66ab0bf2969","tid":825841,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:21:58.000Z","msg":"清潔工同垃圾車司機都係非緊急人員，休咗假邊個幫你掃街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b7758d39ebc4e33faec4f71b7e92b5069cab7f","tid":825841,"uid":144464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:25:33.000Z","msg":"返到工先講有撚用咩"},{"pid":"c67ae54b7a656d882b513cce728d03863904fe33","tid":825841,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:27:04.000Z","msg":"官僚主義，唔想負責任"},{"pid":"f7fe9d852f212f0f0236cfd748b276dbd5cd0168","tid":825841,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:42:44.000Z","msg":"唔駛01 講， 用下腦都知 狗政府根本唔知全港路面有幾多係通幾多係塞<br />\n<br />\n垃圾筒劉江華 同陳帆依啲運房局垃圾局長 理應問責下台"},{"pid":"221c05de46ef508987d5a32869bebeb75537ce2e","tid":825841,"uid":316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:45:56.000Z","msg":"停左市點散得切貨呀"}]}